high_descs: Turn left and walk to the black chair at the desk then turn left to face the desk.
Open the right cabinet door and pick up the book entitled "Learning Spark" and close the cabinet.
Turn left and walk until you're past the desk then turn right and walk to the wall then turn right to face the side of the desk.
Put the book on the desk on the other side of the partition.
Turn around and walk until you're almost to the wall then turn left and walk to the bed.
Pick up the book on the bed entitled "Learning Spark".
Walk back to where you put the first book.
Put the book in your hands to the right of the first book with about half a foot between them.
anns.task_desc: Put two books on the desk.

high_descs: Turn to the left, go to the desk, and look up at the cabinets attached to the desk.
Open the second cabinet from the left and take the book out.
Turn and go to the left end of the desk.
Place the book on the desk.
Turn right and go towards the bed.
Pick up the book from the top of the bed.
Turn around and return to the left end of the desk.
Place the book to the right of the first book on the desk so it is covering the CD on the left.
anns.task_desc: Place two copies of a book on the desk.

high_descs: Walk across the room to the desk.
Open the cabinet above the clock on the desk, take out the magazine, and close the cabinet.
Go to the end of the desk with the trash can.
Set the magazine on the desk behind the clock.
Turn and go across the room to the bed.
Pick up the magazine to the right of the cell phone.
Turn and walk over to the end of the desk with the trash can.
Set the magazine down on top of the disk.
anns.task_desc: Put two magazines on the desk.
